{"tid":384997,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求開解）有冇人都係好驚死","createTime":"2017-09-02T19:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T15:06:57.000Z","uid":136909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4da8bd873fb1ca337cf85e576f3870edf74bfd","tid":384997,"uid":136909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:42:37.000Z","msg":"依個問題我有左好多年，平時日間冇野，但一到夜晚訓之前，就會想死會點，到底係咩都冇，定係真係有天常地獄，越想越驚，越難入睡。<br />\n唔知有冇巴打都係禁，同有咩方法可以令自己唔好驚。<br />\nSorry for 1999。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知個問題好on9，但求解決方法，就算係吹的都得，單純希望比個答題自己，唔好再驚"},{"pid":"f8b0373fef4a58689bde5c922b6323067643760d","tid":384997,"uid":43514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d5c537b3df40ae9aec238e8b95efbac1aa9a60","tid":384997,"uid":87515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:52:51.000Z","msg":"由細個開始已經成日諗<br />\n希望自己唔好死<br />\n<br />\n生存落去最後都係死，咁有咩意思<br />\n要永遠咁生存先體驗到呢個世界"},{"pid":"b3699da581ca995c39f36207f6c2cb6c74f47f37","tid":384997,"uid":128921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:54:24.000Z","msg":"我都好驚，好驚嗰種虛無嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770b2dd0c4378379ca7fa897a4444ab05b2688d8","tid":384997,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T19:55:43.000Z","msg":"我怕生存<br />\n想快啲玩完"},{"pid":"1f25031b3fc8c0918002bde37682d14a7fd81020","tid":384997,"uid":86886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:51:57.000Z","msg":"我以前小學果陣 曾因為時間流逝而傷心<br />\n點要咁快長大 <br />\n人生就係咁 驚死係因為你仲有野想做 仲想很多時間 我覺得人生有d野係必須完成先算不枉此生 就算真係死 都起碼可以回憶人生渺渺。 <br />\n因為到死果刻 你先會後悔當初想做而冇做既事。<br />\n今時今刻 若果大家仲有時間 記得完成人生既目標 可以係旅行 告白女神 食好野"},{"pid":"f82911edf1bfb5549bfdbddd64b2202411256717","tid":384997,"uid":128928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T23:25:01.000Z","msg":"我都好驚死<br />\n有個朋友話佢細個果時遇到鬼，不過係影黎<br />\n如果真係有鬼，就應該會有靈魂存在<br />\n我信我朋友唔會講大話<br />\n但佢果時有冇睇錯或者睇左第二d,誤認為係鬼就好難講<br />\n你地有冇諗過如果撞到鬼未必係壞事<br />\n因為咁可以證明靈魂既存在<br />\n反而未遇過先得人驚"},{"pid":"be11d48fc4d8ef9b36e5d4d7ce0395f72a52931c","tid":384997,"uid":34069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T23:45:29.000Z","msg":"所以我覺得玩rooftopping果啲人真係好撚痴線"},{"pid":"47b36f8a2ed3edf0cac2f69cd375750aad514005","tid":384997,"uid":15406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好驚，好驚嗰種虛無嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame"},{"pid":"f389f8d0188fe3f924c3d3dd134b5a0513989dba","tid":384997,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T23:48:38.000Z","msg":"庸人自擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都始終會死有乜好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cbc6ba5cbe944ba9d2629fa321a56c12785b24","tid":384997,"uid":136909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:10:05.000Z","msg":"推下先，睇下有冇解決左的成功例子"},{"pid":"b9463a84bd9d62f7e63cfc622d533b6a417c84d7","tid":384997,"uid":136909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"我再推"},{"pid":"7f44ada546124c1b7c98d5df66585d20ea0a9510","tid":384997,"uid":38968,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"我呢一排都係諗緊呢啲問題諗到個人好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過慢慢咁諗通咗 因為人係逃避唔到死亡<br />\n活在當下好緊要<br />\n諗通咗 就覺得身邊所有事都好微不足道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好享受同珍惜你而家所擁有嘅野"}]}